name: X [Theme]
shortDescription: Inspired by k.nitsua's NeoStyle I bring you "X". My most complete theme to date and one I'm very proud of. "X" has a unique page layout style and almost every corner has been skinned. X's Lockscreen features ibnyaffa's weather and NEW rss feed that comes with my feed to supply you with "X" theme news, updates, giveaways and more directly on your lockscreen. If your looking for a complete theme that pushes the theme world to another level then this' for you. Thank you for choosing "X"
author: zausser
